query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS stakingRewardsHistory (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  positionId INT NOT NULL,
  userId INT NOT NULL,
  amount DECIMAL(20, 8) NOT NULL,
  asset VARCHAR(20) NOT NULL,
  distributedAt TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  INDEX idx_position (positionId),
  INDEX idx_user (userId),
  INDEX idx_distributed (distributedAt)
);
